 ****************************************************************  225 1451
                                                                   225 1451
New capture cross sections were evaluated with the EDA code.       225 1451
The ENDF/B-VI evaluation is strictly 1/v, going through a low      225 1451
thermal value, whereas the data indicate a higher thermal value,   225 1451
and resonance structure around 2 MeV. This fit also had data in    225 1451
the 4He(gamma,n) direction that indicated a much higher cross      225 1451
section in the MeV region, and that is the reason why the new      225 1451
evaluation looks overshooting the experimental 3He(n,g) data       225 1451
in the MeV region. The differences in the new and old capture      225 1451
cross sections was added to the total cross sections.              225 1451
